realtime.subscription.ix_realtime_subscr.name: ix_realtime_subscription_entity
realtime.subscription.ix_realtime_subscr.sql: CREATE INDEX ix_realtime_subscription_entity ON realtime.subscription USING btree (entity)

realtime.subscription.pk_subscription.name: pk_subscription
realtime.subscription.pk_subscription.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX pk_subscription ON realtime.subscription USING btree (id)

realtime.subscription.subscription_subsc.name: subscription_subscription_id_entity_filters_key
realtime.subscription.subscription_subsc.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX subscription_subscription_id_entity_filters_key ON realtime.subscription USING btree (subscription_id, entity, filters)

storage.buckets.bname.name: bname
storage.buckets.bname.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX bname ON storage.buckets USING btree (name)

storage.buckets_analytics.buckets_analyt.name: buckets_analytics_unique_name_idx
storage.buckets_analytics.buckets_analyt.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX buckets_analytics_unique_name_idx ON storage.buckets_analytics USING btree (name) WHERE (deleted_at IS NULL)

storage.migrations.migrations_name_key.name: migrations_name_key
storage.migrations.migrations_name_key.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX migrations_name_key ON storage.migrations USING btree (name)

storage.objects.bucketid_objname.name: bucketid_objname
storage.objects.bucketid_objname.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX bucketid_objname ON storage.objects USING btree (bucket_id, name)

storage.objects.idx_name_bucket_level_un.name: idx_name_bucket_level_unique
storage.objects.idx_name_bucket_level_un.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_name_bucket_level_unique ON storage.objects USING btree (name COLLATE "C", bucket_id, level)

storage.objects.idx_objects_bucket_id_na.name: idx_objects_bucket_id_name
storage.objects.idx_objects_bucket_id_na.sql: CREATE INDEX idx_objects_bucket_id_name ON storage.objects USING btree (bucket_id, name COLLATE "C")

storage.objects.idx_objects_lower_name.name: idx_objects_lower_name
storage.objects.idx_objects_lower_name.sql: CREATE INDEX idx_objects_lower_name ON storage.objects USING btree ((path_tokens[level]), lower(name) text_pattern_ops, bucket_id, level)

storage.objects.name_prefix_search.name: name_prefix_search
storage.objects.name_prefix_search.sql: CREATE INDEX name_prefix_search ON storage.objects USING btree (name text_pattern_ops)

storage.objects.objects_bucket_id_level_.name: objects_bucket_id_level_idx
storage.objects.objects_bucket_id_level_.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX objects_bucket_id_level_idx ON storage.objects USING btree (bucket_id, level, name COLLATE "C")

storage.prefixes.idx_prefixes_lower_name.name: idx_prefixes_lower_name
storage.prefixes.idx_prefixes_lower_name.sql: CREATE INDEX idx_prefixes_lower_name ON storage.prefixes USING btree (bucket_id, level, ((string_to_array(name, '/'::text))[level]), lower(name) text_pattern_ops)

storage.s3_multipart_uploads.idx_multipa.name: idx_multipart_uploads_list
storage.s3_multipart_uploads.idx_multipa.sql: CREATE INDEX idx_multipart_uploads_list ON storage.s3_multipart_uploads USING btree (bucket_id, key, created_at)

storage.vector_indexes.vector_indexes_na.name: vector_indexes_name_bucket_id_idx
storage.vector_indexes.vector_indexes_na.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX vector_indexes_name_bucket_id_idx ON storage.vector_indexes USING btree (name, bucket_id)

vault.secrets.secrets_name_idx.name: secrets_name_idx
vault.secrets.secrets_name_idx.sql: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX secrets_name_idx ON vault.secrets USING btree (name) WHERE (name IS NOT NULL)
